"The Horde is in maintenance mode, please try again later, if you have tried "
"and the service does not respond for hours, please contact via Discord"
msgstr ""
"Horde sedang dalam mode pemeliharaan, silakan coba lagi nanti, jika Anda "
"sudah mencoba dan layanan tidak merespons selama berjam-jam, silakan hubungi "
