msgid "Prompt for Web Research"
msgstr "Minta Konfirmasi untuk Riset Web"

msgid "Ask for confirmation before sending a web search query"
msgstr "Minta konfirmasi sebelum mengirim kueri pencarian web"

msgid "Web Cache Max Size (MB)"
msgstr "Ukuran Maksimum Cache Web (MB)"

msgid "Max disk size for web search cache (0 to disable)"
msgstr "Ukuran disk maksimum untuk cache pencarian web (0 untuk menonaktifkan)"

msgid "Web Cache Validity (Days)"
msgstr "Validitas Cache Web (Hari)"

msgid "How many days cache entries should be considered valid."
msgstr "Berapa hari entri cache harus dianggap valid."

msgid "Rich Text Control Sidebar"
msgstr "Bilah Samping Kontrol Teks Kaya"

msgid ""
"Formatted chat via RichTextControl (on by default). Requires restart. "
"Uncheck for plain-text chat only."
msgstr ""
"Obrolan terformat melalui RichTextControl (aktif secara default). Perlu "
"mulai ulang. Hapus centang untuk obrolan teks biasa saja."

msgid "Doc"
msgstr "Dok"

msgid "Enable AI grammar checker (Writer)"
msgstr "Aktifkan pemeriksa tata bahasa AI (Writer)"

msgid ""
"When on, WriterAgent registers its AI grammar proofreader with Linguistic; "
"checked text uses your API (Tools → Options → AI). Underlines appear shortly "
"after you pause typing. Off by default."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, WriterAgent mendaftarkan pemeriksa tata bahasa AI-nya ke "
"Linguistik; teks yang diperiksa menggunakan API Anda (Alat → Opsi → AI). "
"Garis bawah akan muncul sesaat setelah Anda berhenti mengetik. Nonaktif "
"secara default."

msgid "Grammar check model (optional)"
msgstr "Model pemeriksaan tata bahasa (opsional)"

msgid "Leave empty to use the same text model as chat."
msgstr "Biarkan kosong untuk menggunakan model teks yang sama dengan obrolan."

msgid "Pause grammar while chat/agent runs"
msgstr "Jeda tata bahasa saat obrolan/agen berjalan"

msgid ""
"When on, AI grammar skips background requests while sidebar chat or agent "
"runs, to avoid concurrent API calls."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, tata bahasa AI melewati permintaan latar belakang saat obrolan "
"bilah sisi atau agen berjalan, untuk menghindari panggilan API bersamaan."

msgid "Grammar batch sentences"
msgstr "Batch kalimat tata bahasa"

msgid ""
"Number of sentences to send per LLM request (1-8). 1 (default) is most "
"reliable; higher values are faster and cheaper but may hit token limits or "
"cause model errors."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah kalimat yang dikirim per permintaan LLM (1-8). 1 (default) adalah "
"yang paling andal; nilai yang lebih tinggi lebih cepat dan lebih murah "
"tetapi dapat mencapai batas token atau menyebabkan kesalahan model."

msgid "Detect and correct sentence language"
msgstr "Deteksi dan koreksi bahasa kalimat"

msgid ""
"When on, asks the AI to verify the language of each sentence against the "
"document's used locales. If incorrect, the language property is updated "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, meminta AI untuk memverifikasi bahasa setiap kalimat terhadap "
"lokal yang digunakan dokumen. Jika tidak tepat, properti bahasa akan "
"diperbarui secara otomatis."

msgid "Enter key sends sidebar chat message"
msgstr "Tombol Enter mengirim pesan obrolan bilah samping"

msgid ""
"When on, Enter in the sidebar query runs the same action as Send; "
"Shift+Enter inserts a newline. When off, Enter inserts a newline."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, Enter pada kueri bilah samping menjalankan tindakan yang sama "
"dengan Kirim; Shift+Enter menyisipkan baris baru. Saat nonaktif, Enter "
"menyisipkan baris baru."

msgid "Draw and Impress tools"
msgstr "Alat Draw dan Impress"

msgid "Core services (config, events, logging)"
msgstr "Layanan inti (konfigurasi, peristiwa, pencatatan)"

msgid "MCP"
msgstr "MCP"

msgid "Enable MCP Server"
msgstr "Aktifkan Server MCP"

msgid ""
"Localhost only, no auth. Clients use http://localhost:<port>/mcp (streamable "
"HTTP)."
msgstr ""
"Hanya localhost, tanpa autentikasi. Klien menggunakan http://localhost:"
"<port>/mcp (HTTP yang dapat dialirkan)."

msgid "MCP Port"
msgstr "Port MCP"

msgid "Allow CORS from local origins"
msgstr "Izinkan CORS dari asal lokal"

msgid ""
"Automatic for .local, .lan, .home.arpa, .internal, .intern, and LAN IPs in "
"the browser Origin. For other hosts, add mcp.cors_allowed_origins in "
"writeragent.json."
msgstr ""
"Otomatis untuk .local, .lan, .home.arpa, .internal, .intern, dan IP LAN di "
"Origin peramban. Untuk host lain, tambahkan mcp.cors_allowed_origins di "
"writeragent.json."

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "Python venv path"
msgstr "Jalur venv Python"

msgid ""
"If set, runs tools in that venv (bin/python or Scripts/python.exe). If "
"empty, run_venv_python_script uses this process's sys.executable (basic "
"stdlib); use a venv for numpy/pandas."
msgstr ""
"Jika diatur, menjalankan alat di venv tersebut (bin/python atau Scripts/"
"python.exe). Jika kosong, run_venv_python_script menggunakan sys.executable "
"proses ini (stdlib dasar); gunakan venv untuk numpy/pandas."

msgid "Test"
msgstr "Uji"

msgid "Python script timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Batas waktu skrip Python (detik)"

msgid ""
"Wall-clock limit for Run Python Script, =PYTHON(), and "
"run_venv_python_script."
msgstr ""
"Batas waktu dinding (wall-clock) untuk Jalankan Skrip Python, =PYTHON(), dan "
"run_venv_python_script."

msgid "Max Calc data cells"
msgstr "Jumlah sel data Calc maksimum"

msgid ""
"Maximum cells in =PYTHON() data or Run Python Script data/data_range. Larger "
"values use more RAM and time; UNO range read still dominates."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah sel maksimum dalam data =PYTHON() atau data/data_range Jalankan Skrip "
"Python. Nilai yang lebih besar menggunakan lebih banyak RAM dan waktu; "
"pembacaan rentang UNO tetap yang paling dominan."

msgid "Python session mode"
msgstr "Mode sesi Python"

msgid ""
"Isolated: each =PYTHON() cell gets a fresh namespace. Shared: one namespace "
"per workbook (variables carry between cells)."
msgstr ""
"Terisolasi: setiap sel =PYTHON() mendapatkan namespace baru. Berbagi: satu "
"namespace per buku kerja (variabel terbawa antar sel)."

msgid "Isolated (default)"
msgstr "Terisolasi (bawaan)"

msgid "Shared kernel"
msgstr "Kernel berbagi"

msgid "Force internal script editor"
msgstr "Paksa penyunting skrip internal"

msgid ""
"If checked, bypasses the Monaco script editor and uses the LibreOffice "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Jika dicentang, melewati penyunting skrip Monaco dan menggunakan dialog "
"LibreOffice."

msgid "Modeless Run Python Script dialog"
msgstr "Dialog Jalankan Skrip Python Tanpa Modal"

msgid ""
"When checked, the plain-text Run Python Script dialog floats so you can edit "
"the document while it is open. Uncheck for the classic modal dialog."
msgstr ""
"Jika dicentang, dialog Jalankan Skrip Python teks biasa akan melayang "
"sehingga Anda dapat menyunting dokumen saat dialog terbuka. Hapus centang "
"untuk dialog modal klasik."

msgid "Writer document tools (including navigation and search)"
msgstr "Alat dokumen Writer (termasuk navigasi dan pencarian)"
